                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d50">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-10-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 9, 1893</hi>
                        </date>. (Received October 10.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson transmits a rumored report that the restoration of monarchy is to be
                    attempted, and announces that the commanding officers of foreign men of war have
                    obtained from the admiral commanding the insurgent vessels a statement that the
                    bombardment of Rio de Janeiro will cease.</p>
            </div>
